document_data.name: Tula Duadil
document_data.mainbody: '''Tula Duadil''' was an [[aquatic elf]] [[thief]] in [[Myth Nantar]].
document_data.History: Tula, a cousin of the ruler of [[Naramyr]], went to the city in order to become a [[dukar]] but was rejected for her power-hungry attitude. Tula wanted revenge, so attempted to insinuate herself into the circles surrounding the [[Nantarn Council]].
document_data.Personality: Tula was a spoiled girl who ruthlessly searched for power.
